      "default": "Cosmic splash screen background for a destiny numerology app, dark navy-to-black gradient, a luminous geometric grid of interconnected circles forming a numerology destiny matrix, each intersection glowing faintly in gold and soft violet, thin light-trail lines linking the nodes like a constellation map, tiny scattered stars and soft light particles, gentle lens flare at the center, elegant and premium mobile app aesthetic, calm and mysterious mood, vertical 9:19.5 composition, no text",
      "required": true,
      "source": "message"
    },
    {
      "key": "width",
      "label": "Width",
      "path": "10.inputs.width",
      "type": "int",
      "default": 960,
      "min": 256,
      "max": 2560,
      "step": 8
    },
    {
      "key": "height",
      "label": "Height",
      "path": "10.inputs.height",
      "type": "int",
      "default": 960,
      "min": 256,
      "max": 2560,
      "step": 8
